1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:11,537
=The Moment I Met You=

2
00:00:11,537 --> 00:00:14,937
=Episode 12=

3
00:00:15,600 --> 00:00:16,719
The Nine-Tailed Fox actually

4
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:18,990
dares to cause trouble
on Sacred Hand Sect's turf.

5
00:00:27,510 --> 00:00:28,399
What are you looking at?

6
00:00:28,399 --> 00:00:29,719
I'll gouge your eyes out!

7
00:00:29,719 --> 00:00:30,320
Move aside.

8
00:00:33,399 --> 00:00:34,640
Including

9
00:00:35,200 --> 00:00:36,079
your brother-in-law,

10
00:00:36,610 --> 00:00:38,079
nearly ten people have gone missing.

11
00:00:38,390 --> 00:00:40,079
Fortunately,
no bodies have turned up yet.

12
00:00:42,320 --> 00:00:43,399
Don't just stand there.

13
00:00:43,719 --> 00:00:44,439
Start searching!

14
00:00:57,960 --> 00:00:58,560
Give me that!

15
00:00:58,560 --> 00:00:59,200
This is...

16
00:00:59,500 --> 00:01:00,390
None of your business.

17
00:01:03,560 --> 00:01:04,799
This sachet has lost its scent.

18
00:01:05,359 --> 00:01:06,599
Why do you still keep it?

19
00:01:07,359 --> 00:01:08,799
My dear Chang gave this to me.

20
00:01:08,879 --> 00:01:10,640
Of course I carry it with me every day.

21
00:01:12,799 --> 00:01:13,640
You men

22
00:01:13,640 --> 00:01:15,200
really are such hypocrites.

23
00:01:15,200 --> 00:01:16,319
If you truly love her,

24
00:01:17,079 --> 00:01:19,079
why don't you keep your distance
from other women?

25
00:01:19,719 --> 00:01:22,000
It's the middle of the night,
we're all alone,

26
00:01:22,079 --> 00:01:23,519
and you're standing so close to me.

27
00:01:23,920 --> 00:01:25,480
You're the one who ambushed me!

28
00:01:26,799 --> 00:01:28,040
I'm talking about

29
00:01:28,799 --> 00:01:29,680
Ms. Mei'er.

30
00:01:29,680 --> 00:01:30,680
I was working a case!

31
00:01:32,400 --> 00:01:33,959
So, for the sake of the case,

32
00:01:34,680 --> 00:01:35,519
it's fine to kiss me?

33
00:01:36,519 --> 00:01:37,959
You kissed me first!

34
00:01:39,560 --> 00:01:40,840
And you just accepted it.

35
00:01:41,159 --> 00:01:43,840
What if some other Squirrels
show up later?

36
00:01:44,079 --> 00:01:45,560
Would you just let them kiss you too?

37
00:01:50,719 --> 00:01:52,439
What? Ran out of excuses?

38
00:01:52,640 --> 00:01:53,760
Now you want to silence me?

39
00:01:54,799 --> 00:01:55,560
You're right.

40
00:01:56,159 --> 00:01:57,400
In the end, I did betray Chang.

41
00:01:57,920 --> 00:01:59,239
I'm going to apologize to her now.

42
00:01:59,920 --> 00:02:01,040
If she won't forgive me,

43
00:02:01,519 --> 00:02:02,560
I'll cut myself

44
00:02:03,200 --> 00:02:05,519
until she forgives me
and still wants to marry me.

45
00:02:07,200 --> 00:02:08,199
Where are you going?

46
00:02:08,199 --> 00:02:09,319
The case isn't closed yet!

47
00:02:15,479 --> 00:02:16,479
What on earth is this?

48
00:02:18,080 --> 00:02:18,919
A suicide note.

49
00:02:19,575 --> 00:02:21,496
You've got to be kidding me.

50
00:02:21,759 --> 00:02:23,039
After everything I just told you,

51
00:02:23,479 --> 00:02:24,840
did you not get it at all?

52
00:02:25,319 --> 00:02:26,479
I'm going to kill you!

53
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:30,400
Ms. Mei'er.

54
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:33,560
If you kill him now,

55
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:35,439
you'd be letting him off too easily.

56
00:02:37,319 --> 00:02:38,319
What do you mean?

57
00:02:39,039 --> 00:02:41,280
I'm an expert at forging handwriting.

58
00:02:41,925 --> 00:02:42,526
How about this?

59
00:02:42,710 --> 00:02:44,639
Give me another
incense stick's worth of time.

60
00:02:44,639 --> 00:02:45,759
I'll mimic his writing

61
00:02:45,759 --> 00:02:47,520
and pen a ransom letter to his family.

62
00:02:47,520 --> 00:02:49,080
Once you have the money,

63
00:02:49,080 --> 00:02:50,840
killing him will be
much more satisfying.

64
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:51,599
Don't you dare!

65
00:03:08,360 --> 00:03:09,280
Who's looking for me?

66
00:03:09,439 --> 00:03:10,439
This little girl here.

67
00:03:11,412 --> 00:03:13,319
(Gate Bureau, Ministry of Justice)

68
00:03:13,319 --> 00:03:14,680
Are you Mao Wenrong?

69
00:03:15,479 --> 00:03:16,120
Yes.

70
00:03:16,520 --> 00:03:18,120
Who are you? What is this about?

71
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:20,439
Someone asked me
to give you this letter.

72
00:03:28,025 --> 00:03:29,129
(Wenrong, my wife. I've been kidnapped.
They want 5,000 taels.)

73
00:03:29,130 --> 00:03:30,234
(Be at Yinding Bridge tomorrow noon
at two o'clock for the exchange.)

74
00:03:30,235 --> 00:03:31,037
(Do not call the guards,
or I'll be executed. From Xu Anran)

75
00:03:33,879 --> 00:03:34,520
Wushuang!

76
00:03:35,319 --> 00:03:36,360
Have you seen Buyu?

77
00:03:36,599 --> 00:03:37,159
What do we do?

78
00:03:37,159 --> 00:03:38,879
It looks like Anran has been taken too.

79
00:03:39,039 --> 00:03:41,000
Buyu was investigating
this case recently,

80
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:42,719
but he's been avoiding me on purpose.

81
00:03:42,719 --> 00:03:43,879
He's being so mysterious.

82
00:03:44,560 --> 00:03:45,520
Don't worry, Rong.

83
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:47,960
As the Chief Coroner of the Gate Bureau,

84
00:03:47,960 --> 00:03:49,960
Anran's scent is unique.

85
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:52,319
We've decided to deploy
all the patrol dogs.

86
00:03:52,319 --> 00:03:54,280
I'm sure we'll find him soon.

87
00:03:54,280 --> 00:03:56,360
I just need a piece of his clothing.

88
00:03:56,360 --> 00:03:57,680
I'll come with you to look.

89
00:03:57,680 --> 00:03:58,800
No need, Rong.

90
00:03:59,400 --> 00:04:01,199
We will definitely
bring Coroner Xu back.

91
00:04:01,199 --> 00:04:02,159
I have to go!

92
00:04:02,562 --> 00:04:05,400
(Wenrong, my wife. I've been kidnapped.
They want 5,000 taels.)

93
00:04:07,439 --> 00:04:09,080
This really is Uncle's handwriting.

94
00:04:09,759 --> 00:04:11,439
Your uncle should be safe for now.

95
00:04:13,080 --> 00:04:14,639
He knows six different styles of script.

96
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:16,319
We have an agreement.

97
00:04:16,319 --> 00:04:17,399
One style means he's safe,

98
00:04:17,399 --> 00:04:19,079
(5,000 taels of gold)
and another means he's in danger.

99
00:04:19,079 --> 00:04:20,279
He uses different handwriting

100
00:04:20,279 --> 00:04:22,040
depending on the situation.

101
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:24,240
Experience really does pay off.

102
00:04:25,240 --> 00:04:26,519
Then what are we waiting for?

103
00:04:26,519 --> 00:04:27,959
Let's storm their hideout

104
00:04:27,959 --> 00:04:28,959
and rescue him!

105
00:04:29,279 --> 00:04:30,639
Do you even know where they are?

106
00:04:31,879 --> 00:04:32,480
Look.

107
00:04:33,000 --> 00:04:34,560
Before the Master left,

108
00:04:34,560 --> 00:04:38,480
he had me use a tracking gu on him.

109
00:04:39,879 --> 00:04:41,079
Why didn't you say so earlier?

110
00:04:41,399 --> 00:04:43,240
The Master told me not to tell you.

111
00:04:43,480 --> 00:04:44,720
He said we should wait for word.

112
00:04:47,240 --> 00:04:49,000
Our best bet is to split up.

113
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:51,680
I'll go to the letter's address
with the money to stall for time.

114
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:53,800
You follow the tracking gu

115
00:04:54,120 --> 00:04:55,120
to where he's being held.

116
00:04:59,512 --> 00:05:02,950
(Zhuyue Nunnery)

117
00:05:06,300 --> 00:05:08,190
The mother bug's wings
are vibrating strangely.

118
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:09,439
He must be in here.

119
00:05:10,279 --> 00:05:11,120
Zhuyue Nunnery.

120
00:05:11,759 --> 00:05:12,680
She turned this place

121
00:05:12,680 --> 00:05:14,279
into a den of iniquity.

122
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:16,279
She really has no fear of heaven.

123
00:05:16,360 --> 00:05:18,600
A wicked woman like her

124
00:05:19,200 --> 00:05:20,720
wouldn't care about divine retribution.

125
00:05:21,040 --> 00:05:21,680
Zhizhi.

126
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:23,680
Go tell Chang to meet us here.

127
00:05:24,000 --> 00:05:25,170
I'm going to scout the area.

128
00:05:33,226 --> 00:05:33,879
Chang.

129
00:05:35,360 --> 00:05:35,920
Chang!

130
00:05:35,920 --> 00:05:37,720
Open the door, we need to talk.

131
00:05:39,040 --> 00:05:40,879
Chang! Chang!

132
00:05:46,639 --> 00:05:48,480
Chang, I'm coming in!

133
00:05:51,920 --> 00:05:52,639
Chang?

134
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:54,680
Chang...

135
00:05:55,199 --> 00:05:56,040
Don't come any closer!

136
00:05:56,279 --> 00:05:57,160
I'm so sorry!

137
00:05:57,560 --> 00:05:58,879
I didn't mean to barge in.

138
00:06:00,279 --> 00:06:00,879
Buyu?

139
00:06:03,560 --> 00:06:04,800
Wait for me outside.

140
00:06:16,079 --> 00:06:16,839
What are you doing?

141
00:06:16,839 --> 00:06:17,399
Move!

142
00:06:18,240 --> 00:06:19,040
Hey, let go!

143
00:06:19,560 --> 00:06:20,160
Wait!

144
00:06:23,199 --> 00:06:24,000
What is going on?

145
00:06:25,160 --> 00:06:26,519
Where are you taking him?

146
00:06:27,879 --> 00:06:29,160
Did his family fail to pay?

147
00:06:35,279 --> 00:06:37,839
Is that you, my dear wife?

148
00:06:38,759 --> 00:06:40,079
How did you know I was here?

149
00:06:40,519 --> 00:06:41,600
You hadn't even arrived,

150
00:06:41,959 --> 00:06:43,879
but your powerful aura

151
00:06:44,120 --> 00:06:45,639
was already overwhelming.

152
00:06:45,879 --> 00:06:46,920
How could I not notice?

153
00:06:47,800 --> 00:06:48,480
Save it.

154
00:06:49,839 --> 00:06:51,519
Weren't you at Zuihong Parlor?

155
00:06:51,680 --> 00:06:54,279
How did you end up a prisoner here?

156
00:06:55,560 --> 00:06:56,959
If I hadn't played the victim,

157
00:06:57,240 --> 00:06:59,240
I never would've
made it into the fox's den.

158
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:03,120
I suspect you were

159
00:07:03,360 --> 00:07:05,759
all too happy to be caught by that thief.

160
00:07:05,920 --> 00:07:07,160
Not at all.

161
00:07:07,519 --> 00:07:10,040
She's nothing compared to you.

162
00:07:10,519 --> 00:07:12,879
I was simply beating them
at their own game.

163
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:16,800
As if I'd believe you.

164
00:07:23,600 --> 00:07:24,279
Looking for me?

165
00:07:26,879 --> 00:07:27,560
Chang.

166
00:07:28,120 --> 00:07:29,639
I missed you so much.

167
00:07:30,319 --> 00:07:31,279
I've done you wrong.

168
00:07:31,279 --> 00:07:32,199
Just hit me.

169
00:07:33,439 --> 00:07:35,079
Why did you drink so much?

170
00:07:35,720 --> 00:07:37,000
My heart is heavy.

171
00:07:38,319 --> 00:07:40,959
Are you going out?

172
00:07:43,120 --> 00:07:43,800
I...

173
00:07:47,959 --> 00:07:48,759
What's that?

174
00:07:49,040 --> 00:07:49,990
What are you looking at?

175
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:51,360
Nothing.

176
00:07:51,639 --> 00:07:53,680
But I really do have an urgent matter.

177
00:07:53,680 --> 00:07:54,959
I need to head out for a bit.

178
00:07:55,639 --> 00:07:57,190
I have something important to tell you!

179
00:07:59,319 --> 00:08:00,079
I'm sorry.

180
00:08:01,240 --> 00:08:02,040
Fine, I understand.

181
00:08:02,040 --> 00:08:03,160
I believe you.

182
00:08:03,160 --> 00:08:03,930
Don't brush me off.

183
00:08:05,319 --> 00:08:06,360
Just let me finish.

184
00:08:09,920 --> 00:08:12,720
I shouldn't have
let that Jade Squirrel kiss me.

185
00:08:13,500 --> 00:08:15,160
But I had no idea
she was going to do it!

186
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:16,160
It happened so fast.

187
00:08:16,160 --> 00:08:17,000
I couldn't react.

188
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:18,079
I didn't know

189
00:08:18,079 --> 00:08:19,879
she was going to kiss me.

190
00:08:20,279 --> 00:08:22,000
Okay, I don't blame you.

191
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:23,959
Our bond is rock solid.

192
00:08:23,959 --> 00:08:25,360
Of course I trust you.

193
00:08:25,720 --> 00:08:27,879
But if you ever see
the Jade Squirrel again,

194
00:08:27,879 --> 00:08:29,519
stay as far away as possible,
understand?

195
00:08:30,199 --> 00:08:32,320
Wait, you know
about the Jade Squirrel too?

196
00:08:34,240 --> 00:08:35,399
Let me tell you this,

197
00:08:35,399 --> 00:08:36,759
but please don't get mad.

198
00:08:37,279 --> 00:08:38,879
Sometimes I feel like

199
00:08:39,039 --> 00:08:42,000
you and that Jade Squirrel are...

200
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:43,679
Sometimes...

201
00:08:44,080 --> 00:08:46,480
I really have to go now.

202
00:08:46,480 --> 00:08:47,120
Buyu.

203
00:08:47,480 --> 00:08:48,919
Go home and get some sleep.

204
00:08:49,110 --> 00:08:50,120
I'm not finished talking!

205
00:08:56,399 --> 00:08:57,720
We're thieves.

206
00:08:58,159 --> 00:08:59,662
We hate nothing more than

207
00:08:59,662 --> 00:09:01,103
lapdogs of the Imperial Court!

208
00:09:01,519 --> 00:09:03,600
Today, I'll take your life

209
00:09:03,879 --> 00:09:05,480
to avenge my martial sister, Lin Xin'er!

210
00:09:05,519 --> 00:09:06,200
Wait!

211
00:09:06,799 --> 00:09:08,080
Before I die,

212
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:09,200
I have one more question.

213
00:09:09,879 --> 00:09:10,759
If you answer me,

214
00:09:11,399 --> 00:09:12,440
then I can die in peace.

215
00:09:13,320 --> 00:09:13,960
Speak.

216
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:16,399
Why did you kill Lin Xin'er,

217
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:17,879
your martial sister?

218
00:09:19,159 --> 00:09:21,679
As thieves, we only care about the money.

219
00:09:22,350 --> 00:09:24,337
Lin Xin'er was far too arrogant.

220
00:09:24,337 --> 00:09:25,530
She wouldn't listen to reason.

221
00:09:25,679 --> 00:09:28,480
She insisted on coming to the Capital
to challenge the Sacred Hand Sect.

222
00:09:29,279 --> 00:09:30,639
She failed and was captured.

223
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:33,080
I didn't really want to kill her.

224
00:09:33,480 --> 00:09:35,887
But the Jade Squirrel scared her so much

225
00:09:35,887 --> 00:09:36,900
that she started babbling.

226
00:09:37,240 --> 00:09:38,790
I couldn't let her implicate the sect,

227
00:09:38,960 --> 00:09:41,080
so I had to purge her.

228
00:09:41,080 --> 00:09:41,720
No.

229
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:43,962
You were afraid
she would expose your presence here

230
00:09:43,962 --> 00:09:44,600
and ruin

231
00:09:44,720 --> 00:09:46,360
your ransom scheme.

232
00:09:49,159 --> 00:09:50,519
For a bookworm,

233
00:09:50,879 --> 00:09:52,639
you're surprisingly sharp.

234
00:09:54,240 --> 00:09:56,480
Fine. Now that you know everything,

235
00:09:56,720 --> 00:09:58,559
you can die in peace.

236
00:09:59,200 --> 00:09:59,840
Miss!

237
00:10:00,320 --> 00:10:01,399
Bad news!

238
00:10:01,759 --> 00:10:02,600
We have a problem!

239
00:10:09,559 --> 00:10:10,200
Where is he?

240
00:10:10,600 --> 00:10:11,279
Where is he?

241
00:10:11,912 --> 00:10:12,552
I...

242
00:10:14,350 --> 00:10:16,512
- Where is he?
- That's all my money!

243
00:10:24,639 --> 00:10:26,240
Madam Zhong! Madam Zhong!

244
00:10:32,519 --> 00:10:33,320
Where is the money?

245
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:35,320
Where is my money!

246
00:10:35,879 --> 00:10:37,000
I don't know.

247
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:37,639
Useless!

248
00:10:38,559 --> 00:10:39,519
You're all useless!

249
00:10:46,840 --> 00:10:48,519
Husband, you're amazing!

250
00:10:48,519 --> 00:10:50,320
I call this "pulling the rug out."

251
00:10:50,679 --> 00:10:53,440
Hu Mei'er's plan just went up in smoke.

252
00:10:57,320 --> 00:10:58,639
Who knocked me out?

253
00:11:05,840 --> 00:11:06,799
Good work, honey.

254
00:11:06,799 --> 00:11:07,639
You too.

255
00:11:11,840 --> 00:11:12,639
Who are you?

256
00:11:13,039 --> 00:11:13,960
What are you doing here?

257
00:11:19,480 --> 00:11:20,639
We're the kidnappers.

258
00:11:21,879 --> 00:11:22,440
Exactly.

259
00:11:22,720 --> 00:11:24,679
We've snatched
the husband of this house.

260
00:11:24,919 --> 00:11:25,960
We're here for the ransom.

261
00:11:25,960 --> 00:11:28,000
So Squire Mei is in your hands.

262
00:11:28,360 --> 00:11:29,039
That's right.

263
00:11:29,879 --> 00:11:31,000
If you want him safe,

264
00:11:31,440 --> 00:11:32,320
don't even resist.

265
00:11:32,799 --> 00:11:33,480
Furthermore,

266
00:11:33,799 --> 00:11:36,080
we also have the girl
from the flower shop.

267
00:11:36,080 --> 00:11:36,720
Chang!

268
00:11:38,519 --> 00:11:39,440
What did you do to her?

269
00:11:39,559 --> 00:11:40,759
Drop your weapon first.

270
00:11:43,799 --> 00:11:45,360
If you dare lay a finger on her,

271
00:11:46,320 --> 00:11:46,960
I swear...

272
00:11:48,159 --> 00:11:49,320
Not again.

273
00:11:52,600 --> 00:11:54,159
Did I mess up again?

274
00:11:58,360 --> 00:11:59,960
Did you steal my money?

275
00:12:01,120 --> 00:12:02,039
Nine-Tailed Fox.

276
00:12:02,240 --> 00:12:03,840
How does it feel to get played?

277
00:12:07,200 --> 00:12:08,679
Jade Squirrel!

278
00:12:13,519 --> 00:12:15,360
The Southern Thieves
and my Martial Alliance

279
00:12:15,400 --> 00:12:16,879
always stay out of each other's way.

280
00:12:17,919 --> 00:12:19,240
But, you've crossed the line.

281
00:12:20,039 --> 00:12:21,440
You stole my money!

282
00:12:23,000 --> 00:12:24,720
It wasn't your money to begin with.

283
00:12:25,559 --> 00:12:26,360
Die!

284
00:12:46,440 --> 00:12:48,720
Who ordered you to kill Lin Xin'er?

285
00:12:49,200 --> 00:12:51,440
She was captured and disgraced our sect.

286
00:12:51,679 --> 00:12:52,600
She deserved to die.

287
00:12:52,679 --> 00:12:54,440
That lie might work on him,

288
00:12:55,000 --> 00:12:56,440
but I know you're taking orders.

289
00:12:56,840 --> 00:12:59,080
You really think
you're so clever, don't you?

290
00:12:59,440 --> 00:13:00,159
The Sacred Token.

291
00:13:00,440 --> 00:13:02,159
Do the Southern Thieves have it?

292
00:13:03,440 --> 00:13:04,720
Give me 100,000 taels of gold

293
00:13:05,000 --> 00:13:06,519
and I'll tell you the truth.

294
00:13:06,879 --> 00:13:08,600
You really are obsessed with money.

295
00:13:44,840 --> 00:13:46,159
Jade Squirrel!

296
00:13:48,399 --> 00:13:49,120
Husband!

297
00:13:49,320 --> 00:13:49,960
Rong.

298
00:13:50,200 --> 00:13:51,240
Go save Coroner Xu.

299
00:13:51,240 --> 00:13:52,279
I'll handle things here.

300
00:13:53,159 --> 00:13:54,440
Anran! Anran!

301
00:13:54,759 --> 00:13:55,720
Wake up!

302
00:13:56,000 --> 00:13:56,639
Anran!

303
00:13:56,759 --> 00:13:57,399
Fire!

304
00:13:57,480 --> 00:13:58,279
No quarter!

305
00:14:07,480 --> 00:14:08,639
Some constable you are.

306
00:14:08,879 --> 00:14:09,919
Resorting to ambushes

307
00:14:10,080 --> 00:14:11,279
and such vicious tactics.

308
00:14:11,600 --> 00:14:13,440
Villains like you deserve no mercy!

309
00:14:25,000 --> 00:14:25,960
Are you two insane?

310
00:14:26,279 --> 00:14:27,639
A constable and a thief

311
00:14:28,080 --> 00:14:29,120
teaming up against me?

312
00:14:29,240 --> 00:14:31,159
I'm going to take your mask off.

313
00:14:31,399 --> 00:14:33,279
I'll kill you first, then her!

314
00:14:44,012 --> 00:14:47,287
♪Grudges and regrets
are like strong wine♪

315
00:14:47,325 --> 00:14:50,200
♪Drink it down and let it go♪

316
00:14:50,700 --> 00:14:56,418
♪An empty cup for our love and hate♪

317
00:14:57,600 --> 00:15:00,920
♪Tears blur a fate I can't control♪

318
00:15:01,050 --> 00:15:03,970
♪Let's drink until dawn♪

319
00:15:05,138 --> 00:15:10,378
♪Behind this mask, I'll never lie♪

320
00:15:11,600 --> 00:15:13,993
♪Every reunion feels like the first♪

321
00:15:13,993 --> 00:15:17,643
♪This hidden smile will never fade♪

322
00:15:17,712 --> 00:15:21,202
♪One heart, standing by your side♪

323
00:15:21,300 --> 00:15:24,275
♪To the ends of time♪

324
00:15:24,275 --> 00:15:27,650
♪The moon traces your face♪

325
00:15:27,837 --> 00:15:31,425
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

326
00:15:31,425 --> 00:15:37,665
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

327
00:15:38,000 --> 00:15:41,215
♪A silent prayer in my soul♪

328
00:15:41,500 --> 00:15:45,038
♪Carrying my vow beneath the moon♪

329
00:15:45,325 --> 00:15:48,350
♪Hoping we never drift apart again♪

330
00:15:48,350 --> 00:15:51,450
♪On our way to forever♪

331
00:15:51,450 --> 00:15:55,300
♪The moon traces your face♪

332
00:15:55,300 --> 00:15:58,660
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

333
00:15:58,850 --> 00:16:04,810
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

334
00:16:05,887 --> 00:16:15,527
♪Just to be with you♪
